(664, 1, '2012-09-27 19:37:17', '2012-09-27 19:37:17', '<img src="http://grovisiblehosting.com/amigos/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/founder.jpg" alt="founder" width="239" height="300" class="alignleft wp-image-6635" />\r\n\r\nAmigos opened for business in Visalia on Dec. 15, 1998.Richared Holguin asked some close friends to help him begin the venture. The friends decided on the name "Amigos" based upon their close friendships and the atmosphere they wished to create within their restaurant.\r\n\r\nRichards infectious smile and wonderful sense of humor created the atmosphere he dreamed of. Richard passed away Aug. 19, 1999 but his dream lived on in a large part thanks to hard work of main chef Grande Aguayo and his wonderful kitchen staff. The kitchen staff is made up of mostly family members who have been with Amigos since it''s opening. The family recipes handed down over generation''s create the authentic taste that have kept loyal customers coming back for years.\r\n\r\nAmigos recently opened in Tulare. The Tulare Amigos features the same great food, sports bar, banquet facilities, take out, delivery and catering. Whether you want to book a party at either location in the banquet room or have your event catered, Amigos offers great food at a very affordable price. Average catered event only costs about 5 - 10 dollars per guest depending on your needs. Please allow us the opportunity to make your next event fun and delicious!', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2013-01-28 15:49:45', '2013-01-28 23:49:45', '', 8, 'http://amigos.pagodabox.com/?page_id=4', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(8, 1, '2012-09-27 19:42:13', '2012-09-27 19:42:13', '<span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: serif;">A</span>migos Sports Bar features numerous televisions so customers can watch a variety of sporting events year round while enjoying Grande''s great mexican food. Amigos truly appreciates it''s customers who come to talk and laugh, eat and drinkin it''s friendly casual atmosphere.Amigos staff works very hard to keep it''s customers coming back by providing consistantly great food and friendly customer service.\r\n\r\n[column size="2x1"]\r\n<h1>Restaurant</h1>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-658" title="visalia-restaurant-one" alt="" src="http://grovisiblehosting.com/amigos/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/visalia-restaurant-one.jpg" width="421" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Large Open Dining</li>\r\n	<li>Delivery</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate Accounts</li>\r\n	<li>Food-To-Go</li>\r\n	<li>Breakfast Sundays 9:00am - 11:00am</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img src="http://grovisiblehosting.com/amigos/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/bottles1.jpg" alt="bottles" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6637" width="421" />\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-659" title="visalia-restaurant-two" alt="" src="http://grovisiblehosting.com/amigos/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/visalia-restaurant-two.jpg" width="421" />\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column size="2x1" last="true"]\r\n<h1>Cantina</h1>\r\n<img class="alignnone  wp-image-649" title="tulare-cantina" alt="" src="http://grovisiblehosting.com/amigos/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/tulare-cantina.jpg" width="421" height="281" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sports Bar</li>\r\n	<li>DirecTV Sports Package</li>\r\n	<li>Gabriels Menudo</li>\r\n	<li>Our Famous Bloody Mary''s</li>\r\n	<li>All-Day Happy Hour</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class="alignnone  wp-image-640" title="tulare-catering" alt="" src="http://grovisiblehosting.com/amigos/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/tulare-catering.jpg" width="422" height="282" />\r\n<img class="alignnone  wp-image-648" title="visalia-restaurant" alt="" src